org.sql: SELECT reactions.* FROM reactions WHERE reactions.reactable_id = "$1" AND reactions.reactable_type = "$2" AND reactions.user_id = "$3" AND reactions.category IN ("$4", "$5")

rewrites.sql: SELECT reactions.* FROM reactions WHERE reactions.reactable_id = "$1" AND reactions.reactable_type = "$2" AND reactions.user_id = "$3" AND reactions.category IN ("$4", "$5") LIMIT 1
